content:
An opinion poll released on Sunday, June 19, showed that DP William Ruto would beat his counterpart Raila Odinga in the 1st round if the General Election was held today.

George Wajackoyah would bag 1.9% while David Mwaure would come in last with 0.7% of the vote.
renderedContent:
